In a further set of experiments, we synthesized NaYF4:Yb/Er@NaYF4 and NaGdF4:Yb/Tm@NaGdF4:Eu UCNPs of ~20 nm in diameter (Fig. 2a, Supplementary Fig. 2 and 3)40,41. Upon 980 nm excitation, Er3+-activated UCNPs showed yellow-green emission with two characteristic bands centered around 540 and 654 nm. For UCNPs coactivated with Tm3+/Eu3+ dopants, characteristic bands centered around 450 and 614 nm were observed, arising from 1D2 \documentclass[12pt]{minimal}
